{
  "id": "adv_card_yu_11_01_short",
  "title": "鈴村優 1話 全人類キュン死間違いなしや！ (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ある日の打ち合わせにて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――During a meeting one day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 1.6000000318
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "……もし恋の新作？　第四弾？\nうちがそのヒロインに……抜擢！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…A new “Moshikoi” game? The fourth installment?\nI’m being chosen as the heroine…!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.1333333652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。シリーズが好調で、新作の打診があったんだ\n優も以前から出たいって言ってたし、良かったら――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. The series is doing well‚ so they offered a new game.\nYou’ve said you wanted to be in it before‚ so if you’re interested—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.8333333652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.5000000001
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "やった～！　めっちゃ嬉しい！\nもちろん引き受けます、ヒロイン役！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yay~! I’m so happy!\nOf course‚ I’ll take it—the heroine role!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.8666666985,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.9666666668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "いや～、やっぱやりたいことは\n常日頃から口に出しとくもんやな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well~ as I thought‚ the things I want to do\nare things you should always say out loud~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.2333333652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "運命の気まぐれか、はたまたうちのポテンシャルの\n賜物か……決まる時はこうして決まるんやな！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whether it’s fate’s whim‚ or a gift of my potential…\nthis is how it gets decided when the time comes!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.4333333652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.0666666668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "優はもし恋がリリースされた当初から\nずっと自分も出たいって言ってたしな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since Moshikoi was first released‚\nYou’s always said you wanted to be part of it‚ Yu",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.5333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　だってめっちゃ面白いやん、もし恋！\nうち、こういうノベルゲー大好きやからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! Because Moshikoi is super fun!\nI love visual novels like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.9333333652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃん、渚ちゃん、芽衣ちゃんの過去三作も\nしっかりやり込んで全エンド回収済みやし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thoroughly completed all the endings\nof the past three installments of Rei-chan‚ Nagisa-chan‚ and Mei-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.0333333652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.0000000001
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "うちにもヒロイン役の話こんかな、出たいな～\nってめっっっちゃ期待してたんよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was seriously looking forward to it‚ like\n“Will I get the heroine role too? I want to be in it!”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.699961366,
